body.name: Prite Tote Bag for Women Weekender Bag with Laptop Compartment for Work Nurse School Travel Gym
features: 【LAPTOP COMPARTMENT】 Safely carry your computer on the go with the laptop compartment, providing hook&loop fastener and padded protection for your valuable device

【SPACIOUS CAPACITY】 16" X 13" X 5.5" in dimension; With ample storage space, this tote bag with more pockets can accommodate a variety of items, from work essentials to school supplies and travel belongings, allowing for easy organization and access

【STYLISH, DURABLE & RAINPROOF】 Made from high-quality materials that offer a sleek and modern design, durability, and waterproof protection; perfect for busy professionals, students, and healthcare workers, it keeps your belongings safe and dry in wet weather while adding a touch of style to your travels

【CONVENIENT ORGANIZATION】 The tote comes with multiple pockets and compartments, allowing you to easily organize and access your belongings. It includes a dedicated laptop sleeve, pen holders, and other pockets for your small items, keeping everything in its place
【VERSATILE TOTE】This tote is not only suitable for work or school, but also perfect for travel or other outdoor activities. Its versatility makes it a practical and stylish companion for you
body.description: This versatile tote offers a stylish design, spacious capacity, durable materials, convenient organization, and versatility, making it the perfect travel companion for professionals, students, and travelers who value both style and functionality. Get yours today and elevate your travel experience!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I use this bag for work. I got tired of carrying a lunch bag, purse, and water bottle/coffee cup. This was the solution! I put my lunch bag, wristlet, 40oz water jug, 16oz coffee cup, among other things (small notebook, kindle, small lotion bottle, pens, etc). There are three pockets inside, two drink pockets (one on either end) and two others, one front (zippered) and one back. There’s so much room for everything. This bag could be used for school, the gym/athletics, or even as a diaper bag. Awesome product and great price. Quality seems to be good so far, as well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I initially bought this bag to use for work in the hospital. It’s sturdy, holds A LOT, and it can be washed. I love it so much, that I’m ordering another one for a different job. I like the way it looks and I love all of the compartments. I recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love this bag!
reviews.reviewText: I am so happy with this bag. I needed it to carry laptop, notebooks, and misc to my church where I volunteer. It is made very well & has pockets where you need them. I will gladly purchase another one in a different color. You won’t be sorry if you buy one of these bags and the price is wonderful. I looked at name brand bags triple to quadruple the price and not nearly as nice.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 22, 2023
reviews.reviewText: My wife Love the fact this bag is waterproof and super roomy & comfortable too carry around , only dislike she had is she wish it had more pockets that’s all but other then day it’s an everyday work bag for her .

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy bag with lots of pockets
reviews.reviewText: I love this bag- it is big enough to haul all of my stuff to work and I can even fit my small purse inside as well. My only complaint is I wish there were different designs/colors as it isn’t a very stylish bag but other than that, it meets my needs!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great bag, worth it
reviews.reviewText: My Daughter needed a new bag for nursing and picked this as a Christmas gift and she loves it, lots of space and good quality

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Good but the Zipper broke already
reviews.reviewText: This tote bag is really nice and worth the money. The only thing I am annoyed about is I've only had it for about 3-4 months and the Zipper broke already. Aside from that, the quality is very nice. The bag is 100% waterproof. Would recommend especially if you are going to take it to school or work.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sooo much better in person
reviews.reviewText: This by far is the most professional, trendy, adorable, everything wrapped up in one computer/tote bag. I absolutely love this bag-it holds my 15.3 Mac perfectly. just cannot begin to tell you how great it is…buy one!!!
